A Tasty Meal for Four

If you (or the kids and babysitter) would rather dine at home, we've put together a tasty meal for you!
1 lb seasoned ground beef or pulled chicken (or a combo of the two), 12 soft flour tortillas, 1 lb Mexican rice and your choice of 1 lb refried, charro or black beans.
Chips and Salsa are included in the pack. Lettuce, tomato and cheese on the side.
